xfce4-fsguard-plugin: Panel Plugin: FSGuard
xfce4-fsguard-plugin:
xfce4-fsguard-plugin: The FSGuard panel plugin checks free space on a chosen mount point
xfce4-fsguard-plugin: frequently and displays a message when a limit is reached. There are two
xfce4-fsguard-plugin: limits: a warning limit where only the icon changes, and an urgent limit
xfce4-fsguard-plugin: that advise the user with a message. The icon button can be clicked to
xfce4-fsguard-plugin: open the chosen mount point. The amount of free space is visible in a
xfce4-fsguard-plugin: tooltip. 
